  "desc": "A member of the decentralized criminal organization that has footprints all over the continent and even deep within unknown domains.<br/>Though they are called \"marksmen,\" this name has an undercurrent of mockery to it, as they use crossbows instead of bows, which require a long period of training to use. It must be said that even hilichurls know how to operate a crossbow. Just point the wider end at the enemy, pull the trigger, and bam — that's all there is to it.",
